Expand description

Views are the panels shown in the viewer’s viewport and the primary means of inspecting & visualizing previously logged data.

In addition to the data that it contains via SpaceViewContents, each view has several view properties that configure how it behaves. Each view property is a crate::Archetype that is stored in the viewer’s blueprint database.
